creator: University of Kentucky
descriptionHtml:
The official University of Kentucky app is a must-have for fans headed to campus or following the Wildcats from afar. With free live audio, exclusive video, and all the scores and stats surrounding the game, the UK Athletics app covers it all!

Features Include:

+ Mobile Ticketing - Access and manage your tickets for Wildcat sports

+ Live Game Audio - Listen to free live audio for football games and other sports throughout the school year

+ On Demand Video – Exclusive coverage of your favorite teams

+ Scores & Stats - All the scores, stats, and play-by-play information that fans need and expect during live games

+ Notifications - Custom alert notifications to let fans know everything surrounding Gameday
